	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Ad me hisce diebus scripsit d. <persName ref="p8417">Musculus</persName> in hęc verba: "In praesenti hoc abs te scire cupio, an gratum tibi futurum sit, si transferaris <placeName ref="l582">Zofingam</placeName> in locum d. <persName ref="p20907">Ieorgii</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Die Berufung von <persName ref="p20907">Jörg Joachim</persName> nach <placeName ref="l1104">Wynigen</placeName> wurde widerrufen; s. Pfister, Die Präd. d. bern. Aarg. S. 141f, Nr. 1115f (irrtüml. Joh. Georg Will; vgl. Nachtr. zu <bibl source="b1">HBBW I</bibl>-X).</note>; nam ille translatus est ad aliam quandam ecclesiam, et vacat illius locus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Quamprimum fieri potest, significa michi animum tuum; neque enim causa ista moram ferre potest" etc.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Super hac <persName ref="p8417">Musculi</persName> petitione cupio ex animo sententiam tuam audire; hanc, quam primum potueris, michi significa, charissime frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Praesentium lator in <placeName ref="l2472">Poloniam</placeName> proficiscitur, pernoctavit apud me; videtur michi valde doctus esse et rerum Christi cupidissimus; tu illum suscipe pro tua in peregrinos charitate.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale, amice incomparabilis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Date <placeName ref="l285">Lentzburgi</placeName> 16. septembris 1553.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p8440">Gervasius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Fideli Christi servo d. <persName ref="p495">Heynricho Bullingero</persName>, amico veteri et fratri in Christo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
